snippet.title: Johnny Depp's wife Amber Heard faces prison over dog smuggling
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's wife Amber Heard has been charged with illegally bringing the couple's dogs to Australia, with her importation charges carrying a maximum penalty of 10 years in prison.
